%% live-feed session state machine.
stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> idle
  idle --> starting: start-live<br/>(new sessionId)
  starting --> negotiating: SDP offer sent
  negotiating --> streaming: answer + ICE,<br/>DTLS connected
  negotiating --> idle: timeout / error
  streaming --> streaming: stats + keepalive
  streaming --> disconnected: transport drop
  disconnected --> streaming: recovered within<br/>grace window
  disconnected --> stopped: grace expired
  streaming --> stopped: stop-live
  stopped --> idle: teardown done
  stopped --> [*]

  note right of negotiating
    Stale answers/ICE for
    old sessionId are ignored.
  end note
